org.mule.modules.sapbobi

Class SapbobiConnector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mule.modules.sapbobi.SapbobiConnector

  • @RequiresEnterpriseLicense(allowEval=true)
 @Connector(name="sapbobi",
           friendlyName="SAP BO BI Metadata Connect",
           minMuleVersion="3.8")
 @RequiresEntitlement(name="sapbobi",
                     provider="Information-asset")
public class SapbobiConnector
extends Object

    SAP BO BI METADATA CONNECTOR

    SAP BusinessObjects (BO) Business Intelligence offers different tools for reporting and analysis purpose. These tools provide full suite of Business Intelligence reporting solution. The connector allows to fetch the Metadata from the Repository. This Connector is used to fetch the Metadata of Universes from Information Design Tool and Metadata of Documents and Reports from Web Intellegence Tool.
    Author:
    Information Asset,llc.
